# Core API Keys
# ===============

# GitHub Personal Access Token (Required)
# Used for: Repository operations, API access
# Create at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Anthropic Claude API Key (Optional)
# Used for: AI-powered features in your development workflow
# Enables: Claude AI code review, security scanning, and other AI features
# Get from: https://console.anthropic.com/account/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Optional API Keys
# =================

# Context7 API Key (Optional)
# Used for: Enhanced documentation lookup and context retrieval
CONTEXT7_API_KEY=your-context7-key

# Brave Search API Key (Optional)
# Used for: Web search capabilities
# Get from: https://api.search.brave.com/app/keys
BRAVE_API_KEY=your-brave-key

# OpenAI API Key (Optional)
# Used for: Alternative AI provider support
# Note: If provided, configure Roo to use either Claude or GPT
# Get from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Firecrawl API Key (Optional)
# Used for: Advanced web scraping and content extraction
# Get from: https://www.firecrawl.dev/app/api-keys
FIRECRAWL_API_KEY=your-firecrawl-key

# Jira Integration Configuration
# Define your Jira project key pattern(s)
# This is used by the commit-msg hook to auto-append Jira keys to commit messages
# 
# Examples:
# Single project key:
# JIRA_PROJECT_KEY="SE"
#
# Multiple project keys (using regex OR):
# JIRA_PROJECT_KEY="SE|PROJ|ABC"
#
# Default pattern (matches any 2-10 uppercase letters):
# JIRA_PROJECT_KEY="[A-Z]{2,10}"